Achievements.Name: Master of the Blade
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete all batting lessons and challenges.

Achievements.Name: Master with the Ball
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete all of the bowling lessons and challenges.

Achievements.Name: Dynamite in the Field
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete all of the fielding lessons.

Achievements.Name: Raise the Bat
Achievements.Description: Score 50 runs in an innings with a single batsman in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Big 100
Achievements.Description: Score 100 runs in an innings with a single batsman in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Double Ton
Achievements.Description: Score 200 runs in an innings with a single batsman in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Triple Ton
Achievements.Description: Score 300 runs in an innings with a single batsman in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Ashes King with the Bat
Achievements.Description: Score 500 runs in an Ashes Series with a single batsman in single player.

Achievements.Name: Power Hitting
Achievements.Description: Hit 6 fours in 6 consecutive deliveries in an innings in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Blazing Blade
Achievements.Description: Hit 6 sixes in 6 consecutive deliveries in an innings in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Hat Trick
Achievements.Description: Take 3 wickets in a row from one bowler in a match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: The Top Hat Trick
Achievements.Description: Take 4 wickets in a row from one bowler in a match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Raise the Ball
Achievements.Description: Take 5 wickets in an innings with a single bowler in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: If You Want Something Done Right
Achievements.Description: Take 10 wickets in an innings with a single bowler in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Nought and Nought
Achievements.Description: Dismiss a batsman for a duck twice in a Test Match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: King Pair
Achievements.Description: Dismiss a batsman for a golden duck twice in a Test Match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Ashes Destroyer
Achievements.Description: Take 40 wickets in an Ashes series with a single bowler in single player.

Achievements.Name: Demolition with the Ball
Achievements.Description: Bowl the opponent out in 10 overs or less in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: ODI Domination
Achievements.Description: Score 300 runs or more in an innings of an ODI Match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Test Match Domination
Achievements.Description: Score 600 runs or more in an innings of a Test Match in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: 10 Wicket Defeat
Achievements.Description: Win a Test Match by 10 wickets in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: Innings Defeat
Achievements.Description: Win a Test Match by an innings or more in single player or ranked online match.

Achievements.Name: ODI Champions
Achievements.Description: Win a full-length ODI Tournament in single player.

Achievements.Name: 20 Over Champions
Achievements.Description: Win a full-length 20 Over Tournament in single player.

Achievements.Name: Ashes Champions
Achievements.Description: Win an Ashes series in single player.
